=========================================================================
Model Attribution
=========================================================================

Neural-signal-to-text transcription uses a derived BCI-trained whisper
model. The bci-embedder.bin weight file contains day-specific projection
matrices derived from the BrainWhisperer research project
(https://github.com/cffan/neural_seq_decoder). End users must obtain
the upstream research checkpoint and convert it locally using
scripts/convert-model.py; no model weights are distributed with this
package.
